Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野獸爆發 跳吧 飛吧 沖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你為什麼要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼盯著人家看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比剛才更快了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他喝的藥裡 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含有什麼特殊的成分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺厲害的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一動起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…就有種怪怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來我似乎睡著了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本就沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是…忍者的精髓所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱老師 我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又中計了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你以為我在這裡就能睡大覺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會在這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是單純喝醉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就毫無痛苦地送你到那個世界去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷得這麼重 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續呆在水裡會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼砍不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易痛痛快快地睡上一覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋真夠吵的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很厲害嗎 過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的動作…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如您所知 所謂醉拳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝得越多 醉得越厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳法的威力就越強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在飯館
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當小李把酒和水搞混後喝了一丁點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和寧次兩人聯手 才勉強制服了李
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人沒能制服他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他是敵人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然能制服他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是總不能讓這麼可愛的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身受重傷啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過喝了小小一杯就醉成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他把整瓶酒都喝掉的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就無敵了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他才剛出院不久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體到底能支撐多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用的是醉拳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是頭一次見到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊方式依然是橫衝直撞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無規律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且速度奇快無比
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春熱血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出他的行動規律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能打到我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厲害的體術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的攻擊能力是骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的分身小鬼告訴過你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就讓你醒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可…沒喝醉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就讓你清醒一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒醉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還沒成年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子是不可以喝酒的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的血繼限界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快思考對策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定還有取勝之道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本跑不遠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又追上來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋暈乎暈乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這傷口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來 我剛才似乎喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副模樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的酒醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的血繼限界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血繼…限界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的血繼限界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以自由地操縱骨細胞和破骨細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連鈣的濃度 形成骨頭的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人的身體裡有兩百多塊骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言 骨頭的數量並不固定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 骨頭終究是骨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折斷它就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是人類的骨頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐松之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完蛋了 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次是阿斯瑪救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次出現危機被救的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是100%啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能幻想有人來幫我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味逐漸飄遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的上衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎忽略了平日所熟悉的自身氣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是用它消除了自己的氣味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚氣味的性質啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我沒能察覺到你的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 兵分兩路來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一手還真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才開始動真格的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是盡可能地拖住這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須避免可能導致自身毀滅的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不使用絕招根本不是他的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然剛做了手術 並不是最佳狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只開八門遁甲的第一門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一門 開門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表蓮華
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用骨頭抵消了這一腳的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼想 都沒什麼好對策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的出現 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你這只喪家之犬\N連嚷嚷的力氣都沒有了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死到臨頭還笑什麼笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們這一次是友軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的同盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂之…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說砂之國與木葉重歸舊好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初我們並非自願攻擊木葉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這次一樣 只是完成任務罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
